metadata.name: Red domineering and unhappy
metadata.description:
The Russian title: «Красный властный и несчастный».

Life leads to the fact that you have to start from scratch at any age. And the pain of loss creates a spiritual experience from which it is impossible to come out the same.

The ZEROING series, inspired by the experience of multiple starts from scratch, both in professional and personal life, reflects human feelings about the need to start all over again.

Resolution: 600
Dimensions: 8000 × 11698
Digitally created
